long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sora Image To Video - Arting AI, a cutting-edge browser extension that revolutionizes video creation. 

With Sora Image To Video, you can upload a image and harness the power of AI to generate a  video based on the uploaded content. 

Simply follow these steps: 
1. Upload your original image; 
2. Input a prompt, then click the generate button; 
3. View the results and download your newly generated video. 

Sora Image To Video - Arting AI streamlines the video editing process and unleashes your creativity like never before!
